					"documentation": "# Show Sale Flow of events\n\n## Basic Flow\n\n1. *Erregistratua* Sale **key**.\n2. *Sistema* displays the information associated to a **Sale** with this *saleNumber* **key** (**title**, **description**, **status**, **price**,**publicationDate** and **file**).  \n3. *erregistratua* baldin bada, *sistemak* **Sale** hori erosteko eta faboritota gehitzeko aukera emango dio.  \n## Alternative flow\n1. Balio gabekoitik edozein eremua badago, eremua hutsik egongo da.\n\n",
					"attributes": [
						{
							"_type": "UMLAttribute",
							"_id": "AAAAAAGcmYFgNU1+aYo=",
							"_parent": {
